// Update UI Tool
// Applies a partial patch to the currently displayed browser UI without a full re-render.
// Sends the patch to the server which broadcasts the update to connected clients.

API base URL is configured via PORT (default 3737) and HOST (default localhost) environment variables.

FUNCTION buildUrl(path, project, session) -> string
  Construct an absolute URL with project and session as query parameters.

---

FUNCTION updateUI(project, session, patch) -> string                             EXPORT
  Validate that patch is a non-null, non-array object.
  POST to /api/update-ui with the patch payload.
  Throw if the request fails. Return JSON string with { success: true, message }.
